practices that our culture,

00:02:39.310 --> 00:02:42.340 align:middle line:84%
our religions, our
countries, through schooling,

00:02:42.340 --> 00:02:45.640 align:middle line:84%
through education,
through media infuse us

00:02:45.640 --> 00:02:49.223 align:middle line:84%
in terms of what is the right
way to function in the world.

00:02:49.223 --> 00:02:50.890 align:middle line:84%
Now, post-World War
II, the culturescape

00:02:50.890 --> 00:02:54.110 align:middle line:84%
was really about rebuilding,
about being safe.

00:02:54.110 --> 00:02:56.620 align:middle line:84%
But in today's
world, we are safe.

00:02:56.620 --> 00:02:59.110 align:middle line:84%
And so in today's world,
the millennial generation,

00:02:59.110 --> 00:03:02.710 align:middle line:84%
the big thing that they want
to pursue is self-discovery,

00:03:02.710 --> 00:03:04.010 align:middle line:90%
is creation.

00:03:04.010 --> 00:03:07.570 align:middle line:84%
The problem is the culturescape
keeps engulfing us and telling

00:03:07.570 --> 00:03:09.220 align:middle line:84%
us that we need
a college degree,

00:03:09.220 --> 00:03:12.312 align:middle line:84%
we need to get a good career,
we need to work the 9:00 to 5:00

00:03:12.312 --> 00:03:14.770 align:middle line:84%
