are good enough so we can get

00:03:14.770 --> 00:03:16.900 align:middle line:84%
into graduate school so we can
get that law degree so we can

00:03:16.900 --> 00:03:18.550 align:middle line:84%
make partner in that
law firm so we can

00:03:18.550 --> 00:03:21.880 align:middle line:84%
