a wife, and two kids,

00:03:21.880 --> 00:03:26.720 align:middle line:84%
and then work from 9:00
to 5:00, slave for a wage

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:29.360 align:middle line:84%
so we can save so that
someday when we are 60,

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:31.160 align:middle line:84%
