and see the world.

00:03:31.160 --> 00:03:34.060 align:middle line:84%
But the thing is, those
rules don't apply anymore.

00:03:34.060 --> 00:03:36.340 align:middle line:84%
The culturescape was
designed to keep us safe,

00:03:36.340 --> 00:03:39.010 align:middle line:84%
but it was never designed
to keep us happy.

00:03:39.010 --> 00:03:40.690 align:middle line:84%
