goals conform to us,

00:04:29.260 --> 00:04:31.200 align:middle line:84%
to what our soul
wants to discover,

00:04:31.200 --> 00:04:34.780 align:middle line:84%
to what we want to
experience on Planet Earth.

00:04:34.780 --> 00:04:37.510 align:middle line:84%
The danger with goal-setting
is very often the goals

00:04:37.510 --> 00:04:40.030 align:middle line:90%
that you set are not your goals.

00:04:40.030 --> 00:04:41.830 align:middle line:84%
They are the
culturescape's definition

00:04:41.830 --> 00:04:45.055 align:middle line:84%
of how you are meant to
be safe in the world.

00:04:45.055 --> 00:04:48.150 align:middle line:84%
But that is one of the
surest paths the misery,

00:04:48.150 --> 00:04:50.200 align:middle line:84%
to waking up one day at
the age of 40 going, what

00:04:50.200 --> 00:04:52.000 align:middle line:90%
the hell happened to my life?

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.040 align:middle line:84%
