And that's why it's
so important for us

00:10:16.510 --> 00:10:20.530 align:middle line:84%
to ensure that we are looking
within to identify what beliefs

00:10:20.530 --> 00:10:22.660 align:middle line:84%
we have about ourselves
and our world,

00:10:22.660 --> 00:10:25.690 align:middle line:84%
and being able to ask
ourselves, is this really true.

00:10:25.690 --> 00:10:27.910 align:middle line:84%
